name: Subsonic Multi-threading
description:
“Cyberspace. A consensual
hallucination experienced daily by
billions of legitimate operators, in
every nation, by children being taught
mathematical concepts... A graphic
representation of data abstracted
from banks of every computer in the
human system. Unthinkable
complexity. Lines of light ranged in
the nonspace of the mind, clusters
and constellations of data. Like city
lights, receding...” ― William Gibson,
Neuromancer
